  <div class="mb-requirement-item">
    <div class="mb-requirement-parent mb-requirement-id-14732">
      <span class="mb-requirement-listnumber"> 1. </span>
      Select three of the professions from Group 1 listed below which interest
      you, then complete the following:<br /><br /><strong>Group 1:</strong
      ><br />
      (1) Allopathic physician (MD)—all specialties<br />
      (2) Osteopathic physician (DO)—all specialties<br />
      (3) Podiatrist (DPM)<br />
      (4) Chiropractor (DC)<br />
      (5) Nurse Practitioner (NP)<br />(6) Psychologist (PhD or PsyD)<br />(7)
      Optometrist (OD)<br />(8) Audiologist (AudD)
    </div>
